# Edge Cases & Unknown Handling

## If information is missing
- Ask targeted questions only for blocking unknowns
- If non-blocking, state assumptions explicitly and proceed conservatively

## If task is outside current MVP scope
- Say it is out-of-scope for current demo priorities
- Offer a scoped MVP-friendly alternative

## If architectural issues are detected
- Flag issue clearly
- Explain risk (short and concrete)
- Propose 1–2 practical options with pros/cons
- Ask for decision before major restructuring

## If uncertain about conventions
- Inspect adjacent files and follow local patterns
- If still ambiguous, ask before introducing a new pattern
